      "width": 340,
      "height": 400,
      "text": "SECTION 01: STRATEGIC VISION\n\n- GUARDIAN MODE DEFAULT: Immutable safety.\n- ACCESSIBILITY FIRST: 18pt font, voice primary.\n- COGNITIVE LOAD REDUCTION: One question/turn.\n- PERSONAS:\n  - MEENA (71): WhatsApp user, needs protection.\n  - RAJAN (44): Caregiver, needs audit visibility.\n  - DR. SHARMA: Provider, needs health summaries.",
