    {
      "id": "text-arch",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 430,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 400,
      "text": "SECTION 02: 5-LAYER PIPELINE ARCHITECTURE\n\n1. INPUT: WhatsApp/Voice -> Scam Filter (Layer 1)\n2. GATEWAY: Private Cloud VPC (No Public Ports)\n3. AGENT CORE: Claude 4.6 (Sonnet) reasoning.\n4. ACTION LAYER: Lobster Deterministic Flows.\n5. EXTERNAL: Verified Health APIs / Caregiver Hub.\n\nHYBRID MODEL: Native Apps <-> Private Cloud Backend",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "box-safety",
