      "x": 920,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 400,
      "text": "SECTION 03: SAFETY & LOBSTER ENGINE\n\nHIGH-STAKES ACTION FLOW:\n1. User Request (Medication/Financial)\n2. LLM Intent Classification\n3. LOBSTER Workflow Activation (Typed YAML)\n4. APPROVAL GATE: Caregiver App push notification.\n5. EXECUTION: Only after human resumeToken.\n\nTHREAT MODEL: SCAM DETECTION FILTER\n- Financial urgency analysis\n- Impersonation signal checks\n- Automated Quarantine",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left"
    },
    {
