      "y": 600,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 280,
      "text": "SECTION 04: THREE-TIER MEMORY ARCHITECTURE\n\n1. HOT (LLM Context): <32K Tokens (Current session)\n2. WARM (Episodic): Qdrant Vector DB (Summarized history)\n3. COLD (Structured): Postgres (Medications, Contacts)\n\nCONTEXT ROT PREVENTION:\n- Hard Token Caps @ Gateway level.\n- Proactive Summarization via Claude Haiku.\n- 77% COST REDUCTION: From $16/user to ~$3.71/user.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left"
    },
