      "text": "SECTION 05: PHASED EXECUTION ROADMAP\n\nPHASE 1 (FOUNDATION): Guardian safety, Voice UI, 5 Workflows.\nPHASE 2 (EXPANSION): Healthcare APIs, Multilingual (Hindi, Tamil),\nABDM Compliance Proxy.\nPHASE 3 (ECOSYSTEM): Power User Tier, Signed Skill Registry,\nDeveloper SDK.\n\nSUCCESS METRIC: <$5 Monthly Cost | >94% Scam Recall.",
